From: Folia Compatibility Patch
Subject: [PATCH 0005] Repeating-Mechanics: Migrate RepeatingTrigger and UserRepeaters to FoliaScheduler.Task

AE PATCH REASON: Repeating enchantment triggers use incompatible BukkitTask management
AE PATCH FIX: Migrate RepeatingTrigger and UserRepeaters to FoliaScheduler.Task
AE PATCH RISK: HIGH
AE PATCH EXCLUDES: net/advancedplugins/ae/impl/effects/effects/mechanics/triggers/internal/RepeatingTrigger.class, net/advancedplugins/ae/impl/effects/effects/mechanics/triggers/internal/RepeatingTrigger$*.class, net/advancedplugins/ae/impl/effects/effects/mechanics/triggers/internal/UserRepeaters.class

---
